ARGUMENT

| Step | Hyp | Ref | Expression |
|---|---|---|---|

| 1 |  | #P_fdm | |- ( F : A --> B -> dom F = A ) |
| 2 | 1 | #P_eqcomd | |- ( F : A --> B -> A = dom F ) |
| 3 | 2 | #P_ineq2d | |- ( F : A --> B -> ( C i^i A ) = ( C i^i dom F ) ) |
| 4 | 3 | #P_reseq2d | |- ( F : A --> B -> ( F |` ( C i^i A ) ) = ( F |` ( C i^i dom F ) ) ) |
| 5 |  | #P_frel | |- ( F : A --> B -> Rel F ) |
| 6 |  | #P_resindm | |- ( Rel F -> ( F |` ( C i^i dom F ) ) = ( F |` C ) ) |
| 7 | 5, 6 | #P_syl | |- ( F : A --> B -> ( F |` ( C i^i dom F ) ) = ( F |` C ) ) |
| 8 | 4, 7 | #P_eqtrd | |- ( F : A --> B -> ( F |` ( C i^i A ) ) = ( F |` C ) ) |
